```plantuml
@startuml UnoSD_UnoCash

actor User
participant "Blazor Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Azure API Management" as APIM
participant "Azure Functions" as Functions
participant "Azure Table Storage" as TableStorage
participant "Azure Blob Storage" as BlobStorage
participant "Azure Form Recognizer" as FormRecognizer

User -> Frontend: Accesses application
Frontend -> APIM: Requests authentication
APIM -> Frontend: Returns auth token

User -> Frontend: Submits expense with receipt
Frontend -> APIM: POST /api/expenses (with receipt data)
APIM -> Functions: Forwards request to AddExpense function
Functions -> BlobStorage: Uploads receipt (using SAS token)
Functions -> TableStorage: Stores expense metadata
Functions -> FormRecognizer: Submits receipt for processing
FormRecognizer -> Functions: Returns parsed receipt data
Functions -> TableStorage: Updates expense with parsed data
Functions -> APIM: Returns success response
APIM -> Frontend: Returns success
Frontend -> User: Shows confirmation

User -> Frontend: Requests expense list
Frontend -> APIM: GET /api/expenses
APIM -> Functions: Forwards to GetExpenses function
Functions -> TableStorage: Queries expenses
TableStorage -> Functions: Returns expense data
Functions -> APIM: Returns formatted response
APIM -> Frontend: Returns expense list
Frontend -> User: Displays expenses

@enduml
```